imdb.plot outline: "Saddle Up!" is a 10 part x 1 hour reality - soap series that follows the day-to-day trials and tribulations of ten business mavericks that attempt to survive life on a working ranch in the pursuit of becoming cowboys - but there's a twist! The series will track the unfolding friendships, the strain of real competition, high stakes, heated romance, mounting pressure and demanding challenges that are unique to the world of ranching.
